channel.description:
Hello everyone my name is Lee I am here from Rune-Server I've been working on a source for awhile that is Project Insanity simply this server does look like shit, but I took it to the next level, and have added many things so far, I really want to take this server to the highest potential I can, throughout that journey I am willing to make new close friends, that would like to develop and run the server with me, below you will find what skills I am interested in, thanks for your time. [i]What Am I Looking For?[/i] - Website Developer Co-Owner [i]Skills Required[/i] - Know how to keep a server clean, I can do all the coding but the question is can you keep it right? Can you keep the server straight the community happy, the forums well active and built? When I plan on releasing this server online to the public, I can see many people just getting so addicted to the server they're going to stay, and that's what I love users staying at an community makes me feel so welcome :) [i]Application[/i] -
